第一戰[[開球儀式|開球儀式]]由前印地安人隊及小熊隊球員{{le|肯尼·洛夫頓|Kenny Lofton}}作為開球貴賓投出第一球<ref name="cfp12">{{cite news|last=Meisel|first=Zack|title='95 reunion: Kenny Lofton, Carlos Baerga to throw out ceremonial first pitches before World Series games in Cleveland|url=http://www.cleveland.com/tribe/index.ssf/2016/10/cleveland_indians_world_series_2.html|accessdate=2016-10-26|work=[[誠懇家日報|誠懇家日報]]|publisher=[[先進出版公司|先進出版公司]]|date=2016年10月25日|location=克里夫蘭|archive-date=2018年8月31日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180831141728/https://www.cleveland.com/tribe/index.ssf/2016/10/cleveland_indians_world_series_2.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。雙方的[[先發投手|先發投手]]分別是[[柯瑞·克魯伯|柯瑞·克魯伯]]（印地安人隊）及[[喬恩·萊斯特|喬恩·萊斯特]]（小熊隊）<ref>{{cite news|last=Assenheimer|first=Chris|title=World Series notes: Cy Young candidates Corey Kluber and Jon Lester set to square off in Game 1|url=http://www.chroniclet.com/tribe-notes/2016/10/24/Indians-notes-Cy-Young-candidates-Kluber-and-Lester-set-to-square-off-in-Game-1.html|accessdate=2016-10-26|work=The Chronicle-Telegram|publisher=[[Elyria-Lorain_Broadcasting_Co.|Elyria-Lorain Broadcasting Co.]]|date=2016-10-24|location=Cleveland|archive-date=2018-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181106142816/http://www.chroniclet.com/tribe-notes/2016/10/24/Indians-notes-Cy-Young-candidates-Kluber-and-Lester-set-to-square-off-in-Game-1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 [[凱爾·舒瓦伯|凱爾·舒瓦伯]]在季賽第四場比賽中扭傷左腳[[韌帶|韌帶]]後就錯過了幾乎整年球季，但在本屆世界大賽第一戰中，他以[[指定打擊|指定打擊]]的身分重返先發<ref>{{cite news|last1=D'Onofrio|first1=Jessica|last2=Elgas|first2=Rob|last3=Horng|first3=Eric|last4=Jordan|first4=Karen|last5=Nagy|first5=Liz|title=Cleveland Indians defeat Chicago Cubs 6–0 in World Series Game 1|url=http://abc7chicago.com/sports/kyle-schwarber-listed-on-chicago-cubs-world-series-2016-game-1-lineup/1572014/|accessdate=2016-10-26|work=[[WLS-TV|ABC 7 Chicago]]|publisher=[[American_Broadcasting_Company|ABC, Inc.]]|date=2016-10-25|location=Cleveland|archive-date=2018-08-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180831141223/https://abc7chicago.com/sports/kyle-schwarber-listed-on-chicago-cubs-world-series-2016-game-1-lineup/1572014/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=McGraw|first=Daniel|title=Indians win World Series Game 1 against Cubs as Kluber sets strikeout record|url=https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2016/oct/25/corey-kluber-cleveland-indians-chicago-cubs-game-1-world-series|accessdate=2016-10-26|work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|date=2016-10-25|location=Cleveland|archive-date=2019-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190414014204/https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2016/oct/25/corey-kluber-cleveland-indians-chicago-cubs-game-1-world-series|dead-url=no}}</ref>。舒瓦伯被三振兩次，但也打出一支二壘安打並獲得一次保送上壘<ref>{{cite news|last=Reiter|first=Ben|title=Kyle Schwarber's successful return a silver lining for Cubs in Game 1 loss|url=https://www.si.com/mlb/2016/10/26/world-series-kyle-schwarber-return-chicago-cubs|accessdate=2016-10-26|work=[[Sports_Illustrated|Sports Illustrated]]|date=2016-10-26|location=Cleveland|archive-date=2020-06-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200606214133/https://www.si.com/mlb/2016/10/26/world-series-kyle-schwarber-return-chicago-cubs|dead-url=no}}</ref>。這支二壘安打讓舒瓦伯成為投手以外，首位在世界大賽裡打出季賽首安的選手<ref>{{cite web|last=Snyder|first=Matt|title=Cubs-Indians 2016 World Series: Kyle Schwarber's return, at least, was a success|url=http://www.cbssports.com/mlb/news/cubs-indians-2016-world-series-kyle-schwarbers-return-at-least-was-a-success/|publisher=[[CBSSports.com|CBSSports.com]]|accessdate=2016-10-26|location=Cleveland|date=2016-10-26|archive-date=2020-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200414233801/https://www.cbssports.com/mlb/news/cubs-indians-2016-world-series-kyle-schwarbers-return-at-least-was-a-success/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

克魯伯在前三局就三振了八個打席，創下世界大賽的新紀錄<ref>{{cite web|last=Marchand|first=Andrew|title=Corey Kluber sets World Series record with 8 K's in first 3 innings|url=http://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/17888355/corey-kluber-cleveland-indians-sets-world-series-strikeout-mark|publisher=[[ESPN|ESPN]]|accessdate=2016-10-26|location=Cleveland|date=2016-10-26|archive-date=2019-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190413074549/http://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/17888355/corey-kluber-cleveland-indians-sets-world-series-strikeout-mark|dead-url=no}}</ref>。印地安人隊的[[羅伯托·佩雷斯|羅伯托·佩雷斯]]在本戰中打出雙響砲，成為史上首位在世界大賽中達成此紀錄的九棒打者、印地安人隊隊史上首位在世界大賽雙響砲球員，以及首位在世界大賽打出雙響砲的波多黎各裔球員<ref>{{cite news|last=Berg|first=Ted|title=Indians catcher Roberto Perez has as many homers this October as he had all season|url=http://ftw.usatoday.com/2016/10/cleveland-indians-roberto-perez-two-homers-game-1-world-series-mlb|accessdate=2016-10-26|work=[[USA_Today|USA Today]]|date=2016-10-26|location=Cleveland|archive-date=2019-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190413105341/https://ftw.usatoday.com/2016/10/cleveland-indians-roberto-perez-two-homers-game-1-world-series-mlb|dead-url=no}}</ref>。小熊隊先發投手萊斯特第一局一開始就先被打一支一壘安打又送出兩次保送，奉送印地安人隊滿壘局面，接著[[荷西·拉米瑞茲|荷西·拉米瑞茲]]打出一壘安打送回一分，然後萊斯特對{{le|布蘭登·蓋耶爾|Brandon Guyer}}投出觸身球又送回一分。第四局佩雷斯的陽春砲讓印地安人隊取得3：0領先。到了第八局，小熊隊中繼投手[[賈斯汀·格林|賈斯汀·格林]]兩出局後先保送了蓋耶爾，然後又被[[朗尼·奇森霍爾|朗尼·奇森霍爾]]敲出一壘安打，然後接替格林投球的{{le|海克特·朗登|Hector Rondon}}被佩雷斯敲出當晚的第二發全壘打。儘管[[安德魯·米勒_(棒球員)|安德魯·米勒]]在第七局陷入滿壘的危機，他最終還是和[[柯迪·艾倫|柯迪·艾倫]]一同守住最後三局，幫助印地安人隊在系列賽的第一戰中以6：0獲勝<ref>{{cite news|last=Nightengale|first=Bob|title=Magic formula: Corey Kluber, Andrew Miller dominant in Game 1 World Series win over Cubs|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/mlb/columnist/bob-nightengale/2016/10/26/corey-kluber-andrew-miller-world-series-game-1-indians-cubs/92757694/|accessdate=2016-10-26|work=[[USA_Today|USA Today]]|date=2016-10-26|location=Cleveland|archive-date=2017-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170928193330/https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/mlb/columnist/bob-nightengale/2016/10/26/corey-kluber-andrew-miller-world-series-game-1-indians-cubs/92757694/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。印地安人隊總教練弗蘭克納在世界大賽的連勝場次也推進到九場<ref>{{cite web |author1=Andrew Simon |title=Francona perfect at 9-0 in World Series |url=https://www.mlb.com/news/indians-terry-francona-9-0-in-world-series-c207176548 |website=mlb.com |accessdate=2020-08-27 |archive-date=2022-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220110044745/https://www.mlb.com/news/indians-terry-francona-9-0-in-world-series-c207176548 }}</ref>。

[[德克斯特·佛勒|德克斯特·佛勒]]在第一局的登場讓他成為小熊隊史上第一位登上世界大賽舞台的非裔美國籍球員<ref>{{cite news|title=Dexter Fowler 1st African-American Chicago Cub to start in Game 1 of World Series|url=http://wgntv.com/2016/10/24/dexter-fowler-becomes-first-black-chicago-cub-in-world-series/|publisher=[[WGN-TV|WGN-TV]]|date=2016-10-24|accessdate=2017-07-14|archive-date=2018-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180611072539/http://wgntv.com/2016/10/24/dexter-fowler-becomes-first-black-chicago-cub-in-world-series/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Breen|first=Justin|title=Dexter Fowler Would Be The First Black Cubs Player In The World Series|url=https://www.dnainfo.com/chicago/20161024/wrigleyville/dexter-fowler-first-black-cub-world-series|website=[[DNAinfo.com|DNAinfo Chicago]]|date=2016-10-24|accessdate=2017-07-14|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170522065937/https://www.dnainfo.com/chicago/20161024/wrigleyville/dexter-fowler-first-black-cub-world-series|archivedate=2017-05-22|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

