第二戰的開球貴賓是前印地安人隊球員{{le|卡洛斯·貝爾加|Carlos Baerga}}<ref name=cfp12/>。由於天氣預報顯示將有大雨的可能，因此本站提前一小時開打<ref>{{cite news|last1=Footer|first1=Alyson|last2=McCalvy|first2=Adam|title=Game 2 bumped up to 7 ET tonight on FOX|url=http://m.mlb.com/news/article/207155096/game-2-of-world-series-to-start-1-hour-earlier/|publisher=MLB Advanced Media|website=MLB.com|location=Cleveland|accessdate=2016-10-26|archive-date=2017-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170928103121/http://m.mlb.com/news/article/207155096/game-2-of-world-series-to-start-1-hour-earlier/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。小熊隊為了在此戰中扳平系列賽，他們推出[[傑克·艾瑞亞特|傑克·艾瑞亞特]]上投手丘對抗印地安人隊的先發投手[[崔佛·鮑爾|崔佛·鮑爾]]，後者仍在治療因[[崔佛·鮑爾#無人機操作意外|修理無人機]]而割傷的小指。本戰小熊隊先發打線一共有六位球員未滿25歲，創下大聯盟季後賽紀錄<ref>{{cite web|last=Anderson|first=R.J.|title=Cubs-Indians World Series Game 2: Final score, things to know as Cubs even series|url=http://www.cbssports.com/mlb/news/cubs-indians-world-series-game-2-final-score-things-to-know-as-cubs-even-series/|publisher=[[CBSSports.com|CBSSports.com]]|accessdate=2016-10-27|date=2016-10-26|archive-date=2016-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161028023718/http://www.cbssports.com/mlb/news/cubs-indians-world-series-game-2-final-score-things-to-know-as-cubs-even-series/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。小熊隊第一局先靠[[克里斯·布萊恩|克里斯·布萊恩]]一壘安打上壘，接著[[安東尼·瑞佐|安東尼·瑞佐]]的二壘安打送回布萊恩先馳得點，1：0領先<ref>{{cite web|last=Doolittle|first=Bradford|title=Next stop: Chicago! Cubs trounce Tribe, even World Series|url=http://www.espn.com/blog/sweetspot/post/_/id/76013/next-stop-chicago-cubs-trounce-tribe-even-world-series|publisher=[[ESPN|ESPN]]|accessdate=2016-10-27|location=Cleveland|date=2016-10-27|archive-date=2016-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161028083729/http://www.espn.com/blog/sweetspot/post/_/id/76013/next-stop-chicago-cubs-trounce-tribe-even-world-series|dead-url=no}}</ref>。先發投手艾瑞亞特開局表現也很好，一局下半面對的頭兩名打者都解決出局，雖然後面連續保送兩名打者，但最終以飛球出局結束這個半局。三局上半，小熊隊靠著瑞佐獲得保送以及[[班·佐布里斯特|班·佐布里斯特]]的一壘安打站上得點圈。接著[[凱爾·舒瓦伯|凱爾·舒瓦伯]]的一壘安打送回了瑞佐，小熊隊取得2：0領先。鮑爾在四局上半被迫退場，而小熊隊在第五局攻勢又起，瑞佐面對印地安人隊投手{{le|薩克·麥克艾利斯特|Zach McAllister}}又獲得保送，隨後佐布里斯特的三壘安打將瑞佐送回得分<ref>{{cite news|last=Graves|first=Will|title=Rizzo, Zobrist lead Cubs' offensive outburst in Game 2|url=http://bigstory.ap.org/article/0249b1d62cbd4a3fb4371c9f70253886/rizzo-zobrist-lead-cubs-offensive-outburst-game-2|accessdate=2016-10-27|agency=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]|date=2016-10-27|location=Cleveland|archive-date=2017-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170103031821/http://bigstory.ap.org/article/0249b1d62cbd4a3fb4371c9f70253886/rizzo-zobrist-lead-cubs-offensive-outburst-game-2|dead-url=no}}</ref>。下一棒舒瓦伯面對{{le|布萊恩·蕭 (棒球)|Bryan Shaw (baseball)|布萊恩·蕭}}擊出一壘安打再添一分，後在形成滿壘的情形下，[[艾迪生·羅素|艾迪生·羅素]]獲得保送又擠回壘上跑者得一分，小熊隊來到5：0的領先<ref>{{cite news|last=Nightengale|first=Bob|title=Kyle Schwarber defying odds, leads Cubs offense in Game 2 of World Series|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/mlb/columnist/bob-nightengale/2016/10/26/cubs-kyle-schwarber-world-series-game-2/92809568/|accessdate=2016-10-27|work=[[USA_Today|USA Today]]|date=2016-10-27|location=Cleveland|archive-date=2017-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170928193415/https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/mlb/columnist/bob-nightengale/2016/10/26/cubs-kyle-schwarber-world-series-game-2/92809568/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

艾瑞亞特在後續局數繼續表現可圈可點，六局前僅保送三人而未被打出任何安打<ref>{{cite news|last=Wagner|first=James|title=Cubs Pull Even in World Series as Indians' Play Proves Sloppier Than the Weather|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2016/10/27/sports/baseball/jake-arrieta-chicago-cubs-beat-cleveland-indians-world-series-game-2.html|accessdate=2016-10-27|newspaper=[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]|date=2016-10-27|location=Cleveland|archive-date=2016-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161031043145/http://www.nytimes.com/2016/10/27/sports/baseball/jake-arrieta-chicago-cubs-beat-cleveland-indians-world-series-game-2.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。但[[傑森·基普尼斯|傑森·基普尼斯]]第六局的二壘打終結了前者無安打的局面，接著他又靠著{{le|滾地球|Ground out (baseball)}}上到三壘，最後在艾瑞亞特整場好投中跑回印地安人隊唯一的一分<ref>{{cite web|last=Reiter|first=Bill|title=World Series Game 2: Cubs' Arrieta finds greatness when his team needs it most|url=http://www.cbssports.com/mlb/news/world-series-game-2-cubs-arrieta-finds-greatness-when-his-team-needs-it-most/|publisher=[[CBSSports.com|CBSSports.com]]|accessdate=2016-10-27|location=Cleveland|date=2016-10-27|archive-date=2016-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161028022455/http://www.cbssports.com/mlb/news/world-series-game-2-cubs-arrieta-finds-greatness-when-his-team-needs-it-most/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。艾瑞亞特在被打出另一支一壘安打後，由後援投手[[麥克·蒙哥馬利|麥克·蒙哥馬利]]接替投球。雙方在第七局互有攻勢，但都無功而返。接著八局下半，[[麥克·拿坡里|麥克·拿坡里]]擊出一壘安打後，小熊隊守護神[[阿羅魯迪斯·查普曼|阿羅魯迪斯·查普曼]]登場關門取勝。這場勝利是小熊隊自{{wsy|1945}}以來首場世界大賽賽事的勝利，並成功扳平系列賽<ref>{{cite web|last=Martin|first=Jill|title=Cubs level World Series with first Fall Classic win since 1945|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2016/10/26/sport/world-series-chicago-cubs-cleveland-indians-game-2/index.html|publisher=CNN|accessdate=2016-10-27|date=2016-10-27|archive-date=2016-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161027084103/http://edition.cnn.com/2016/10/26/sport/world-series-chicago-cubs-cleveland-indians-game-2/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而這場敗仗也是印地安人隊總教練[[特里·弗蘭克納|特里·弗蘭克納]]在世界大賽中的首敗<ref>{{cite web |author1=R.J. Anderson |title=Cubs-Indians World Series Game 2: Final score, things to know as Cubs even series |url=https://www.cbssports.com/mlb/news/cubs-indians-world-series-game-2-final-score-things-to-know-as-cubs-even-series/ |website=CBSSPORTS.COM |accessdate=2020-10-16 |date=2016-10-26 |archive-date=2020-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201017041259/https://www.cbssports.com/mlb/news/cubs-indians-world-series-game-2-final-score-things-to-know-as-cubs-even-series/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

