第三戰，前小熊隊球員[[比利·威廉斯|比利·威廉斯]]作為開球貴賓投出第一球，喜劇演員[[比爾·莫瑞|比爾·莫瑞]]則在{{le|第七局中場休息|seventh-inning stretch}}時演唱「[[帶我去看棒球賽|帶我去看棒球賽]]」，以致敬小熊隊在世界大賽的第一場晚間主場賽事<ref>{{cite news|last=De Luca|first=Chris|title=Billy Williams, Bill Murray part of historic World Series Game 3|url=http://chicago.suntimes.com/sports/billy-williams-bill-murray-part-of-historic-game-world-series-3/|accessdate=2016-10-29|work=[[Chicago_Sun-Times|Chicago Sun-Times]]|date=2016-10-28|archive-date=2019-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190403220057/https://chicago.suntimes.com/sports/billy-williams-bill-murray-part-of-historic-game-world-series-3/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。雙方的先發投手分別是[[凱爾·漢崔克斯|凱爾·漢崔克斯]]（小熊隊）及{{le|賈許·湯姆林|Josh Tomlin}}（印地安人隊）。

本戰唯一的一分出現在七局上半，印地安人隊的[[可可·克里斯普|可可·克里斯普]]打出一支一壘安打，將三壘上的{{le|邁克爾·馬丁內斯|Michael Martínez}}送回得分。印地安人隊的投手群{{le|賈許·湯姆林|Josh Tomlin}}、[[安德魯·米勒_(棒球員)|安德魯·米勒]]、{{le|布萊恩·蕭 (棒球)|Bryan Shaw (baseball)|布萊恩·蕭}}及[[柯迪·艾倫|柯迪·艾倫]]聯手[[完封|完封]]了小熊隊<ref>{{cite news|last1=Mather|first1=Victor|last2=Waldstein|first2=David|title=World Series: Here's What Happened in Game 3|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2016/10/28/sports/world-series-score-cubs-indians.html|accessdate=2016-10-29|newspaper=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|date=2016-10-28|archive-date=2016-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161118232305/http://www.nytimes.com/2016/10/28/sports/world-series-score-cubs-indians.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="2016WSGame1">{{cite news|last1=Bastian|first1=Jordan|last2=Muskat|first2=Carrie|title=Blank you very much! Tribe 1–0 W epic|url=http://m.mlb.com/news/article/207475482/indians-shut-out-cubs-in-world-series-game-3/|publisher=MLB Advanced Media|website=MLB.com|accessdate=2016-10-29|location=Chicago|date=2016-10-29|archive-date=2017-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171128221105/http://m.mlb.com/news/article/207475482/indians-shut-out-cubs-in-world-series-game-3/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。艾倫在九局下半讓[[哈維爾·巴耶茲|哈維爾·巴耶茲]]揮棒落空三振出局結束了比賽，留下得點圈有超前分的殘壘，並取得他生涯中第六次季後賽救援成功的紀錄。這也是小熊隊在216年季後賽期間第四次被完封而敗的比賽<ref name="2016WSGame1" />。

