本次世界大賽第七戰將是場經典，有人稱其為世界大賽歷史上最偉大的第七戰，並將其與{{wsy|1960}}、{{wsy|1991}}和{{wsy|2001}}的戲劇性和張力相比<ref>{{cite news|last=Foster|first=Jason|title=The 10 most memorable Game 7s in World Series history, ranked|url=http://www.sportingnews.com/mlb/list/world-series-2016-greatest-game-7-in-world-series-history-twins-giants-yankees-braves-diamondbacks/7i1zz6sbin9c1c0vtss28999s#|accessdate=2016-12-23|publisher=[[Sporting_News|Sporting News]]|location=Chicago|archive-date=2018-07-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180718080728/http://www.sportingnews.com/mlb/list/world-series-2016-greatest-game-7-in-world-series-history-twins-giants-yankees-braves-diamondbacks/7i1zz6sbin9c1c0vtss28999s|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Armour|first=Nancy|title=Why Cubs, Indians just gave us greatest World Series Game 7 ever|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/columnist/nancy-armour/2016/11/03/chicago-cubs-win-game-7-world-series-cleveland-indians/93224558/|accessdate=2016-12-23|publisher=[[USA_Today|USA Today]]|location=Chicago|archive-date=2019-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191222151903/https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/columnist/nancy-armour/2016/11/03/chicago-cubs-win-game-7-world-series-cleveland-indians/93224558/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。第七戰的開球貴賓是前印地安人隊球員[[吉姆·湯米|吉姆·湯米]]<ref>{{cite news|last=Meisel|first=Zack|title=Jim Thome to throw out ceremonial first pitch prior to Game 7 of the World Series|url=http://www.cleveland.com/tribe/index.ssf/2016/11/cleveland_indians_world_series_17.html|accessdate=2016-11-02|work=[[The_Plain_Dealer|The Plain Dealer]]|publisher=[[Advance_Publications|Advance Publications]]|location=Cleveland|archive-date=2018-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612162907/https://www.cleveland.com/tribe/index.ssf/2016/11/cleveland_indians_world_series_17.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。雙方的先發投手，分別是曾代表小熊隊於第三戰先發的季賽[[美國職棒大聯盟防禦率王|防禦率王]][[凱爾·漢崔克斯|凱爾·漢崔克斯]]，以及曾代表印地人隊於第一戰及第四戰先發的[[柯瑞·克魯伯|柯瑞·克魯伯]]，後者僅休息三天便上場。賽前，克魯伯在本季季後賽的戰績為四勝一敗，防禦率0.89<ref>{{cite web|title=Corey Kluber Postseason Statistics|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/gl.fcgi?id=klubeco01&t=p&post=1|publisher=Baseball Reference|accessdate=2020-08-31|archive-date=2017-09-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170903073143/https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/gl.fcgi?id=klubeco01&t=p&post=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[德克斯特·佛勒|德克斯特·佛勒]]第一局首打席面對克魯伯就敲出全壘打，成為第一位在世界大賽第七戰打出首打席全壘打的球員<ref>{{cite news|last=McCalvy|first=Adam|title=Fowler makes history with leadoff HR|url=http://m.mlb.com/news/article/207936946/dexter-fowler-hits-leadoff-homer-in-game-7/|publisher=MLB Advanced Media|website=MLB.com|date=2016-11-02|accessdate=2016-11-03|location=Cleveland|archive-date=2016-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161103012938/http://m.mlb.com/news/article/207936946/dexter-fowler-hits-leadoff-homer-in-game-7/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。印地安人隊在三局下半靠著[[可可·克里斯普|可可·克里斯普]]二壘安打及[[羅伯托·佩雷斯|羅伯托·佩雷斯]]的犧牲觸擊上到三壘，再藉由[[卡洛斯·桑塔納_(棒球員)|卡洛斯·桑塔納]]一分打點的一壘安打追平比數。四局上半，小熊隊一出局一三壘有人，[[艾迪生·羅素|艾迪生·羅素]]打出中外野不遠的飛球被接殺，但三壘跑者[[克里斯·布萊恩|克里斯·布萊恩]]跑壘相當積極，於接殺後從三壘迅速跑向本壘，並滑過捕手的觸殺碰到本壘得分，接著[[威爾遜·康崔拉斯|威爾遜·康崔拉斯]]的二壘安打再添一分，小熊隊3：1領先。五局上半，[[哈維爾·巴耶茲|哈維爾·巴耶茲]]瞄準第一球就打出全壘打將比數改寫為4：1，而克魯伯也被打下投手丘退場<ref>{{cite news|last=DiComo|first=Anthony|title=Baez's homer chases Kluber in Game 7|url=http://m.mlb.com/news/article/207810222/javier-baez-homers-off-corey-kluber-in-game-7/|publisher=MLB Advanced Media|website=MLB.com|accessdate=2016-11-02|location=Cleveland}}</ref>。接替投球的是[[聯盟冠軍賽最有價值球員獎|美聯冠軍賽MVP]][[安德魯·米勒_(棒球員)|安德魯·米勒]]，但她上來先保送了布萊恩，隨後布萊恩又積極盜上二壘，然後米勒又讓[[安東尼·瑞佐|安東尼·瑞佐]]敲出帶有一分打點的一壘安打，比數變成5：1。五局下半，漢崔克斯成功解決前兩名打者，接著保送了桑塔納，說服總教練[[喬·梅登|喬·梅登]]換投。梅登此次決定與系列賽裡的其他指令之後都讓他備受批評{{efn|梅登在九局上半三壘有[[傑森·海沃德|傑森·海沃德]]及兩好球的情形下，依然讓[[哈維爾·巴耶茲|哈維爾·巴耶茲]]進行觸擊，導致後者觸擊成界外球而形成三好球出局，這個舉動也同樣遭受批評}}，因為看起來當時似乎是太早換下<ref>{{cite web|last=Hirsch|first=Sheldon|title=Maddon's Over-Thinking Nearly Cost Cubs|url=http://dev.realclearsports.com/articles/2016/12/19/maddons_over-thinking_nearly_cost_cubs_98476.html|publisher=RealClearSports|accessdate=2016-12-23|location=Cleveland|archive-date=2016-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161224100432/http://dev.realclearsports.com/articles/2016/12/19/maddons_over-thinking_nearly_cost_cubs_98476.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

第一戰及第五戰的先發投手[[喬恩·萊斯特|喬恩·萊斯特]]登場中繼，這是他自[[2007年美聯冠軍賽|2007年美聯冠軍賽]]以來的第一次，而那年碰到的正好也是印地安人隊<ref>{{cite news|last=Stankevitz|first=JJ|title=Jon Lester ready if needed to pitch out of bullpen in games 6 or 7 of World Series|url=http://www.csnchicago.com/chicago-cubs/jon-lester-ready-if-needed-pitch-out-bullpen-games-6-or-7-world-series|accessdate=2016-12-23|publisher=[[CSN_Chicago|CSN Chicago]]|location=Chicago|archive-date=2017-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170816012112/http://www.csnchicago.com/chicago-cubs/jon-lester-ready-if-needed-pitch-out-bullpen-games-6-or-7-world-series|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[大衛·羅斯|大衛·羅斯]]的傳球失誤讓[[傑森·基普尼斯|傑森·基普尼斯]]及壘上的桑塔納分別推進到二壘及三壘。之後萊斯特一個彈到羅斯捕手頭盔上的暴投，讓桑塔納和基普尼斯都回來得分，比數追近到3：5<ref>{{cite news|last1=Williams|first1=Cody|title=World Series 2016: Indians score two on wild pitch, pull closer at 5–3|url=http://fansided.com/2016/11/02/world-series-2016-indians-wild-pitch-score-5-3-video/|accessdate=2016-11-02|work=Fansided|date=2016-11-02|archive-date=2018-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181106145032/https://fansided.com/2016/11/02/world-series-2016-indians-wild-pitch-score-5-3-video/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。六局上半，39歲的羅斯將功贖罪，在他生涯最後一個打數打出全壘打，不只讓小熊隊的領先來到6：3，他本人也成為史上在世界大賽第七戰最年長擊出全壘打的球員<ref>{{cite news|last1=Smith|first1=Alex|title=Former SEC star David Ross makes World Series history in final career game|url=https://www.seccountry.com/florida/former-sec-star-david-ross-makes-world-series-history-in-final-career-game|accessdate=2016-11-02|work=SEC Country|date=2016-11-02|archive-date=2018-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180816025646/https://www.seccountry.com/florida/former-sec-star-david-ross-makes-world-series-history-in-final-career-game|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

到了八局上半，萊斯特先解決了前兩名打者，但在被[[荷西·拉米瑞茲|荷西·拉米瑞茲]]及出一壘安打後被換下。儘管小熊隊當時已領先不少，但梅登總教練仍決定啟用第五戰已投42球且第六戰也曾上場的[[阿羅魯迪斯·查普曼|阿羅魯迪斯·查普曼]]。結果被印地安人隊{{le|布蘭登·蓋耶爾|Brandon Guyer}}剛好打出一支二壘安打送回一分，比數6：4。下一棒是印地安人隊中外野手[[拉傑·戴維斯|拉傑·戴維斯]]，他生涯僅55轟而本季也僅有11轟，且本次季後賽打擊率只有1成32，但他奇蹟似的從查普曼手中敲出兩分砲，這發全壘打僅僅剛好越過左外野全壘打牆及左外野全壘打標竿，將壘上的蓋耶爾一併送回，比數追平成6：6。戴維斯這發全壘打是世界大賽第七戰歷史中，最新一發追平轟<ref>{{cite web|last=Spector|first=Jesse|title=World Series 2016: Rajai Davis' HR becomes footnote to Cubs' epic victory|url=http://www.sportingnews.com/mlb/news/world-series-2016-indians-cubs-rajai-davis-home-run-aroldis-chapman-1986-red-sox-francisco-lindor/2lih0t8hiexz1cf8rjbekqyyd|publisher=SportingNews.com|accessdate=2016-11-03|location=Cleveland|date=2016-11-03|archive-date=2017-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170816000919/http://www.sportingnews.com/mlb/news/world-series-2016-indians-cubs-rajai-davis-home-run-aroldis-chapman-1986-red-sox-francisco-lindor/2lih0t8hiexz1cf8rjbekqyyd|dead-url=no}}</ref>。許多球迷及查普曼本人都認為第六戰不必要的上場讓他搞砸了領先優勢。「28號查普曼表示，他覺得第七戰自己『有點不一樣』，而這個疲勞影響了他自己的表現。{{efn|''Chapman, 28, said he felt ‘a little different’ in Game 7 and that fatigue affected him.''}}」 <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.chicagotribune.com/sports/baseball/cubs/ct-aroldis-chapman-joe-maddon-postseason-20161216-story.html|title=Aroldis Chapman says Cubs manager Joe Maddon 'abused him a bit'|last=Skrbina|first=Paul|website=chicagotribune.com|language=en-US|access-date=2019-02-21|archive-date=2019-02-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190221111952/https://www.chicagotribune.com/sports/baseball/cubs/ct-aroldis-chapman-joe-maddon-postseason-20161216-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

小熊隊搞砸了九局上半的得分機會：[[大衛·羅斯|大衛·羅斯]]首先獲得保送，[[傑森·海沃德|傑森·海沃德]]打出滾地球讓[[代跑|代跑]]的[[克里斯·柯格蘭|克里斯·柯格蘭]]出局，但自己依靠野手選擇上壘。隨後海沃德盜上二壘，再靠著{{le|揚·戈麥斯|Yan Gomes}}傳球給二壘手基普尼斯的失誤上盜三壘。[[哈維爾·巴耶茲|哈維爾·巴耶茲]]試圖在兩好球後進行觸擊，結果點成界外球變兩出局。下一棒[[德克斯特·佛勒|德克斯特·佛勒]]最終打成滾地球，被印地安人隊游擊手[[法蘭西斯科·林多爾|法蘭西斯科·林多爾]]驚人的守下傳一壘抓到第三個出局數，從而結束這個半局<ref>{{cite web |author1=Marcus Hartman |title=7 moments that made Game 7 of the World Series unforgettable |url=https://www.daytondailynews.com/sports/world-series-top-moments-from-the-cubs-game-win-over-the-indians/DMvR8WSQnUnkyBjm5DjkhK/ |website=Dayton Daily News |publisher=Dayton Daily News |accessdate=2020-08-31 |archive-date=2018-01-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180130112703/http://www.daytondailynews.com/sports/world-series-top-moments-from-the-cubs-game-win-over-the-indians/DMvR8WSQnUnkyBjm5DjkhK/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。阿羅魯迪斯·查普曼在九局下半回到投手丘上，及時解決了印地安人隊一二三棒[[卡洛斯·桑塔納_(棒球員)|卡洛斯·桑塔納]]、[[傑森·基普尼斯|傑森·基普尼斯]]及[[法蘭西斯科·林多爾|法蘭西斯科·林多爾]]<ref name="Game7record">{{cite web |title=2016 World Series Game 7, Cubs at Indians, November 2 |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/CLE/CLE201611020.shtml |website=baseball-reference |accessdate=2020-08-31 |archive-date=2020-03-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200301151658/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/CLE/CLE201611020.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

雙方在九局結束後以6：6戰成平手，但突然的[[暴雨|暴雨]]導致{{le|因雨延遲|Rainout (sports)}}了17分鐘<ref name="raindelay7">{{cite news|url=https://www.dnainfo.com/chicago/20161102/wrigleyville/cubs-indians-world-series-game-7-championship|title=Game 7 Of The World Series Is In A Rain Delay In Extra Innings|author1=Ariel Cheung|author2=Ed Komenda|author3=David Matthews|author4=Evan F. Moore|date=2016-11-02|accessdate=2016-11-02|publisher=DNA Info|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161104010916/https://www.dnainfo.com/chicago/20161102/wrigleyville/cubs-indians-world-series-game-7-championship|archivedate=2016-11-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。在延遲期間，小熊隊右外野手[[傑森·海沃德|傑森·海沃德]]將隊友們召集到[[棒球球員休息區|休息區]]後方的舉重室，並跟大家精神喊話「我們是最棒的棒球隊...因為某個原因...將我們聚在一起，而我們將贏下這場比賽{{efn|''We're the best team in baseball. . . for a reason. . . Stick together and we're going to win this game.''}}。」<ref name="WORLD SERIES It Happened">{{cite news|last=Verducci|first=Tom|title=WORLD SERIES It Happened|url=https://www.si.com/vault/2016/11/15/world-series-it-happened|magazine=[[Sports_Illustrated|Sports Illustrated]]|date=2016-11-14|accessdate=2017-01-07|archive-date=2018-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180820113415/https://www.si.com/vault/2016/11/15/world-series-it-happened|dead-url=no}}</ref>

比賽重新開始後的十局上半，[[凱爾·舒瓦伯|凱爾·舒瓦伯]]面對{{le|布萊恩·蕭 (棒球)|Bryan Shaw (baseball)|布萊恩·蕭}}首先擊出右半邊的一壘安打，隨後換上[[代跑|代跑]][[阿爾伯特·阿爾莫拉|阿爾伯特·阿爾莫拉]]。接著[[克里斯·布萊恩|克里斯·布萊恩]]打出中外野的深遠飛球，幫助阿爾莫拉推進到二壘，該次跑壘被稱為「本季最精明的跑壘」{{efn|''savviest baserunning play of the season.''}}<ref>{{cite web|last=Rosenbloom|first=Steve|title=Do you really appreciate what Albert Almora Jr. did in Game 7?|url=http://www.chicagotribune.com/sports/rosenblog/ct-albert-almora-cubs-world-series-rosenbloom-20161104-column.html|publisher=Chicago Tribune|accessdate=2016-12-23|location=Cleveland|archive-date=2018-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181116130339/https://www.chicagotribune.com/sports/rosenblog/ct-albert-almora-cubs-world-series-rosenbloom-20161104-column.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[安東尼·瑞佐|安東尼·瑞佐]]獲得故意保送後，[[班·佐布里斯特|班·佐布里斯特]]站上打擊區。佐布里斯特先前四個打數沒有安打，但這次他打出左外野方向的二壘安打，將阿爾莫拉送回本壘得分，並打破平局將比數改寫為7：6。佐布里斯特後來提到：「我知道他會投切球，我就只是站在打擊區等他的球，但很幸運的，他丟了一個非常靠近本壘板的球，然後我就沿著三壘邊線打過去，而這正是我要的。{{efn|''I was just battling, grinding up there. Fortunately, that last one he left over the plate and up to where I could just slap it down the line, and that was all I was trying to do.''}}」<ref>{{cite news|last=Kepner|first=Tyler|title=With a Cure-Breaking Hit, Ben Zobrist lives a dream he never expected|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2016/11/03/sports/baseball/world-series-game-7-ben-zobrist-chicago-cubs.html|newspaper=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|date=2016-11-03|accessdate=2016-12-23|archive-date=2020-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200104082713/https://www.nytimes.com/2016/11/03/sports/baseball/world-series-game-7-ben-zobrist-chicago-cubs.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Graves|first=Will|title=Zobrist's big hit gives Cubs newcomer World Series MVP|url=http://bigstory.ap.org/article/584762ab80d74b429e8b3a93a3271500/zobrists-big-hit-gives-cubs-newcomer-world-series-mvp|accessdate=2016-11-03|agency=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]|date=2016-11-03|location=Cleveland|archive-date=2017-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170112192333/http://bigstory.ap.org/article/584762ab80d74b429e8b3a93a3271500/zobrists-big-hit-gives-cubs-newcomer-world-series-mvp|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author1=科爾曼 |title=低調的英雄 - 2016World Series MVP: Ben Zobrist |url=https://www.sportsv.net/articles/35546 |website=運動視界 |accessdate=2020-08-31 |archive-date=2022-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220110043814/https://www.sportsv.net/articles/35546 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author1=曹玉烱 |title=絕死第7戰勝利打點 Zobrist獲世界大賽MVP |url=https://tw.sports.yahoo.com/news/%E7%B5%95%E6%AD%BB%E7%AC%AC7%E6%88%B0%E5%8B%9D%E5%88%A9%E6%89%93%E9%BB%9E-zobrist%E7%8D%B2%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E5%A4%A7%E8%B3%BDmvp-062652566.html |website=Yahoo!運動 |accessdate=2020-08-31 |archive-date=2022-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220110042413/https://tw.sports.yahoo.com/news/%E7%B5%95%E6%AD%BB%E7%AC%AC7%E6%88%B0%E5%8B%9D%E5%88%A9%E6%89%93%E9%BB%9E-zobrist%E7%8D%B2%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E5%A4%A7%E8%B3%BDmvp-062652566.html }}</ref>

[[艾迪生·羅素|艾迪生·羅素]]獲得另一次故意保送後，替代羅斯捕手位上場的是[[米格爾·蒙特羅|米格爾·蒙特羅]]，他這個季後賽的打擊率僅0.091。然而他卻打出左半邊的一壘安打，送回瑞佐得分，將比數拉大到8：6。印地安人隊派出在第二戰及第五戰吞敗的[[崔佛·鮑爾|崔佛·鮑爾]]接替蕭上場救援，先三振掉海沃德，再讓巴耶茲擊成飛球出局，成功避免比數差距擴大<ref name="Game7record" />。

十局下半印地安人隊進攻，小熊隊叫上{{le|小卡爾·愛德華茲|Carl Edwards Jr.}}上場關門，但他在解決頭兩名打者[[麥克·拿坡里|麥克·拿坡里]]及[[荷西·拉米瑞茲|荷西·拉米瑞茲]]後，卻保送了{{le|布蘭登·蓋耶爾|Brandon Guyer}}，蓋耶爾更利用防守漏洞盜上二壘。[[拉傑·戴維斯|拉傑·戴維斯]]延續他八局時英雄的表現，打出中間方向的一壘安打，將比分縮小為8：7一分差。梅登總教練接著派出了[[麥克·蒙哥馬利|麥克·蒙哥馬利]]上場救援，後者生涯從未拿過救援成功。但蒙哥馬利成功讓第三戰跑回致勝分的{{le|邁克爾·馬丁內斯|Michael Martínez}}打出內野滾地球，隨後被三壘手布萊恩接到，傳向一壘的瑞佐封殺。比賽結束，世界大賽的勝利者也出爐，由小熊隊贏得冠軍，終結了108年以來的冠軍荒<ref>{{cite news|last1=Bastian|first1=Jordan|last2=Muskat|first2=Carrie|title=Cubs are heavy wait champions!|url=http://m.mlb.com/news/article/207938228/chicago-cubs-win-2016-world-series/|publisher=MLB Advanced Media|website=MLB.com|date=2016-11-02|accessdate=2016-11-02|location=Cleveland|archive-date=2017-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171130223630/http://m.mlb.com/news/article/207938228/chicago-cubs-win-2016-world-series/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Sullivan|first=Paul|title=Chicago Cubs win World Series championship with 8–7 victory over Cleveland Indians|url=http://www.chicagotribune.com/sports/baseball/cubs/ct-cubs-win-world-series-sullivan-spt-1103-20161102-story.html|accessdate=2016-11-03|work=[[Chicago_Tribune|Chicago Tribune]]|date=2016-11-03|location=Cleveland|archive-date=2016-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161104002550/http://www.chicagotribune.com/sports/baseball/cubs/ct-cubs-win-world-series-sullivan-spt-1103-20161102-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[班·佐布里斯特|班·佐布里斯特]]因在世界大賽打出打擊率3成57並在第七戰敲出致勝分，從而被選為[[世界大賽最有價值球員獎|世界大賽最有價值球員獎]]<ref>{{cite news|last=Trezza|first=Joe|title=Zobrist's heroics net MVP honors|url=http://m.mlb.com/news/article/207951690/ben-zobrist-named-world-series-mvp/|publisher=MLB Advanced Media|website=MLB.com|date=2016-11-02|accessdate=2016-11-03|archive-date=2016-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161118220433/http://m.mlb.com/news/article/207951690/ben-zobrist-named-world-series-mvp/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Berg|first=Ted|title=World Series MVP Ben Zobrist: Game 7 was 'an epic battle'|url=http://ftw.usatoday.com/2016/11/ben-zobrist-chicago-cubs-world-series-mvp-epic-battle-mlb|newspaper=[[USA_Today|USA Today]]|date=2016-11-03|accessdate=2016-11-03|location=Cleveland|archive-date=2018-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181106142421/https://ftw.usatoday.com/2016/11/ben-zobrist-chicago-cubs-world-series-mvp-epic-battle-mlb|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==== 第七戰後 ====
瑞佐認為因雨延遲「是芝加哥小熊隊過去一百年來所發生之最重要的事件。我不認為我們有辦法在沒有這事的情形下贏得比賽勝利。{{efn|''the most important thing to happen to the Chicago Cubs in the past 100 years. I don't think there's any way we win the game without it.''}}」小熊隊總管[[西奧·艾普斯坦|西奧·艾普斯坦]]表示當他聽到海沃德所召開的會議後，「當時我在想，我們正要贏得這場比賽。{{efn|''Right then I thought, 'We're winning this game.''}}」<ref name="WORLD SERIES It Happened" />

小熊隊成為自{{wsy|1985}}{{le|1985年堪薩斯皇家隊球季|1985 Kansas City Royals season|堪薩斯皇家隊}}以來，第一支在世界大賽中克服1勝3敗的劣勢獲得最後的冠軍<ref>{{cite web |author1=Andrew Simon |title=From down 3-1, Cubs working on more history |url=https://www.mlb.com/cubs/news/history-of-3-1-world-series-comebacks-c207699942 |website=Mlb.com |accessdate=2020-08-31 |archive-date=2022-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220327001940/https://www.mlb.com/cubs/news/history-of-3-1-world-series-comebacks-c207699942 }}</ref>。他們也是自{{wsy|1979}}{{le|1979年匹茲堡海盜隊球季|1979 Pittsburgh Pirates season|匹茲堡海盜隊}}以來第一支在第六戰及第七戰連勝的客場球隊、第二支在第七戰勝出的客場球隊{{efn|因為{{wsy|2014}}{{le|2014年舊金山巨人隊球季|2014 San Francisco Giants season|舊金山巨人隊}}也曾於客場擊敗{{le|2014年堪薩斯皇家隊球季|2014 Kansas City Royals season|堪薩斯皇家隊}}}}。隔年{{le|2017年休士頓太空人隊球季|2017 Houston Astros season|休士頓太空人隊}}也於[[洛杉磯道奇|洛杉磯]]達成此事，而{{wsy|2019}}{{le|2019年華盛頓國民隊球季|2019 Washington Nationals season|華盛頓國民隊}}也在第七戰客場取勝擊敗{{le|2019年休士頓太空人隊球季|2019 Houston Astros season|休士頓太空人隊}}。小熊隊在第七戰取勝後，連同[[2008年美國聯盟冠軍賽|2008年美國聯盟冠軍賽]]及[[2013年美國聯盟外卡晉級賽|2013年美國聯盟外卡晉級賽]]，[[喬·梅登|喬·梅登]]在季後賽對戰[[特里·弗蘭克納|特里·弗蘭克納]]取得三勝零敗的戰績<ref>{{cite web |title=Joe Maddon Managerial Record _ Baseball-Reference.com |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/managers/maddojo99.shtml |website=Baseball-Reference.com |accessdate=2020-08-31 |archive-date=2020-09-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200917144744/https://www.baseball-reference.com/managers/maddojo99.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Terry Francona Managerial Record _ Baseball-Reference.com |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/managers/francte01.shtml |website=Baseball-Reference.com |accessdate=2020-08-31 |archive-date=2020-08-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200827233833/https://www.baseball-reference.com/managers/francte01.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。本戰是世界大賽史上第六十場打到延長賽的比賽，也是史上第一次有客隊在第七戰延長賽取勝。前四次第七戰打到延長賽的世界大賽包括{{wsy|1912}}、{{wsy|1924}}、{{wsy|1991}}以及{{wsy|1997}}，這四次勝出的都是主場球隊<ref>{{cite web |title=A brief history: Here's every World Series Gm 7 |url=https://www.mlb.com/news/history-of-world-series-game-7-c39984458 |website=mlb.com |accessdate=2020-08-31 |archive-date=2020-04-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200425073849/https://www.mlb.com/news/history-of-world-series-game-7-c39984458 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

印地安人隊輸掉這場比賽以後，他們現在是擁有最長冠軍荒的球隊（截至2020年已經長達72年）。他們上次奪冠已是{{wsy|1948}}，但是當本屆世界大賽開打之際，{{le|克里夫蘭體育魔咒|Cleveland sports curse}}就已因[[2015－16克里夫蘭騎士賽季|騎士隊]]在[[2016年NBA總決賽|NBA總決賽]]中擊敗{{le|2015年-2016年金州勇士隊球季|2015-16 Golden State Warriors season|金州勇士隊}}後被打破，騎士隊也奪得克里夫蘭自1964年以來的首座冠軍獎盃<ref>{{cite news|last=McCauley|first=Janie|title=James and Cavaliers win thrilling NBA Finals Game 7, 93-89|url=http://www.nba.com/games/20160619/CLEGSW/gameinfo.html|agency=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]|publisher=NBA Media Ventures, LLC|date=2016-06-19|accessdate=2017-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160619134342/http://www.nba.com/games/20160619/CLEGSW/gameinfo.html|archive-date=2016-06-19|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Tan|first=Avianne|title=This Cavs Season Ticket Holder Waited 45 Years for a Championship|url=https://abcnews.go.com/Sports/meet-69-year-cleveland-cavaliers-fan-bought-season/story?id=40014126|work=[[ABC_News|ABC News]]|publisher=ABC News Internet Ventures|date=2016-06-21|accessdate=2016-07-12|archive-date=2019-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190320133837/https://abcnews.go.com/Sports/meet-69-year-cleveland-cavaliers-fan-bought-season/story?id=40014126|dead-url=no}}</ref>。如同本次小熊隊的表現，騎士隊也是克服一勝三敗的劣勢，最終在第七戰中以客場球隊身分取勝{{efn|舉行地點為勇士隊主場所在地[[奧克蘭_(加利福尼亞州)|奧克蘭]]}}<ref name="FinalsGame7">{{cite web |url=http://espn.go.com/nba/recap?gameId=400878160 |title=Cavaliers become first team to rally from 3–1 series deficit in NBA Finals |website=ESPN.com |accessdate=2016-06-19 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160627180622/http://espn.go.com/nba/recap?gameId=400878160 |archivedate=2016-06-27 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Withers|first=Tom|title=The End: Cleveland rocks as title drought ends in Finals|url=http://www.nba.com/2016/news/06/19/cleveland-ends-drought.ap/index.html|agency=Associated Press|publisher=National Basketball Association|date=2016-06-19|accessdate=2016-06-20|archive-date=2016-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160928085516/http://www.nba.com/2016/news/06/19/cleveland-ends-drought.ap/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。

