===廣播轉播===
[[File:Cubs_World_Series_win_being_celebrated_at_Wrigley_Field_(2).gif|thumb]]
{{le|ESPN美國職棒大聯盟廣播台|Major League Baseball on ESPN Radio|ESPN電台}}的國家網絡通過附屬電台播報世界大賽，主播及球評分別是{{le|丹·舒爾曼|Dan Shulman}}和[[亞倫·布恩|亞倫·布恩]]<ref name=schedule/>。第一戰及第二戰部分的局數，還邀請[[坦帕灣光芒隊|坦帕灣光芒隊]]投手[[克理斯·亞契|克理斯·亞契]]擔任來賓球評<ref>{{cite press release|url=http://espnmediazone.com/us/press-releases/2016/10/espn-provides-extensive-site-coverage-112th-world-series/|title=ESPN Provides Extensive On-SIte Coverage from the 112th World Series|last=Skarka|first=Michael|publisher=ESPN MediaZone|date=2016-10-24|access-date=2020-09-01|archive-date=2016-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161104011136/http://espnmediazone.com/us/press-releases/2016/10/espn-provides-extensive-site-coverage-112th-world-series/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在各地的廣播，這些隊伍的[[旗艦台|旗艦台]]會與他們的常規播報員一起轉播系列賽。克里夫蘭負責轉播印地人隊的是{{le|WTAM}}（1100）及{{le|WMMS}}（100.7），播報員是{{le|湯姆·漢密爾頓 (播報員)|Tom Hamilton (sportscaster)|湯姆·漢密爾頓}}及{{le|吉姆·羅森浩斯|Jim Rosenhaus}}；而在芝加哥負責轉播小熊隊的是{{le|WSCR}}（670），播報員是{{le|帕特·休斯|Pat Hughes (sportscaster)}}、{{le|羅恩·庫默|Ron Coomer}}及{{le|萊恩·卡斯柏|Len Kasper}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://awfulannouncing.com/2016/your-2016-world-series-announcing-schedule.html|title=Your 2016 World Series announcing schedule|last=Lucia|first=Joe|website=Awful Announcing|date=2016-10-25|accessdate=2020-09-01|archive-date=2016-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161104003419/http://awfulannouncing.com/2016/your-2016-world-series-announcing-schedule.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。根據合約，各隊伍區域無線電網絡的附屬電台有義務轉播ESPN國家廣播節目（national ESPN Radio feed）；但即便如此，由於WSCR和WTAM都是{{le|清晰頻道電台|clear-channel station}}，因此美國東部和中西部的大多數地區都還是能收聽到當地廣播<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cantonrep.com/news/20161026/tom-hamilton-not-heard-on-indians-local-radio-affiliates-during-world-series|title=Tom Hamilton not heard on Indians' local radio affiliates during World Series|last=Kane|first=Dan|newspaper=The Repository|date=2016-10-26|accessdate=2020-09-01|archive-date=2016-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161104000822/http://www.cantonrep.com/news/20161026/tom-hamilton-not-heard-on-indians-local-radio-affiliates-during-world-series|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==慶祝==
[[File:Cubs_at_the_White_House_(01).jpg|thumb]]
第七戰勝出後，小熊隊球迷聚集在[[瑞格利球場|瑞格利球場]]外面與{{le|瑞格利城|Wrigleyville}}周圍慶祝奪冠<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-37856319|title=World Series baseball: Chicago Cubs end 108-year wait for win|date=2016-11-03|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=2016-11-04|archive-date=2018-08-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180831083521/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-37856319|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://ftw.usatoday.com/2016/11/chicago-cubs-world-series-wrigleyville-celebrate-video-photos |title=Wrigleyville goes wild as Chicago Cubs win the World Series |last=Tsuji |first=Alysha |publisher=Gannett Satellite Information Network, LLC |date=2016-11-03 |website=For the Win USAToday |access-date=2016-12-23 |archive-date=2018-11-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181106140013/https://ftw.usatoday.com/2016/11/chicago-cubs-world-series-wrigleyville-celebrate-video-photos |dead-url=no }}</ref>。11月4日，小熊隊的奪冠遊行從瑞格利球場開始，然後沿著市區的湖岸大道（Lake Shore Drive）和密西根大道（Michigan Avenue）遊行，中午時抵達[[格蘭特公園|格蘭特公園]]舉辦大集會<ref>{{cite news|url=http://time.com/4558307/cubs-world-series-parade-live/|title=Watch Chicago Get the World Series Parade It's Waited 108 Years For|date=2016-11-04|work=Time|accessdate=2016-11-04|archive-date=2017-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170703012832/http://time.com/4558307/cubs-world-series-parade-live/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。鄉村歌手{{le|布雷特·埃德雷奇|Brett Eldredge}}在大集會上演唱「{{le|去吧，小熊，去吧|Go, Cubs, Go}}」<ref>{{cite web|title=Watch: Brett Eldridge leads Cubs fans in 'Go Cubs Go'|url=http://www.csnchicago.com/chicago-cubs/watch-brett-eldredge-leads-cubs-fans-go-cubs-go|website=[[Comcast_SportsNet_Chicago|Comcast SportsNet Chicago]]|publisher=[[NBC_Universal|NBC Universal]]|accessdate=2016-11-07|date=2016-11-04|archive-date=2017-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170731120946/http://www.csnchicago.com/chicago-cubs/watch-brett-eldredge-leads-cubs-fans-go-cubs-go|dead-url=no}}</ref>。芝加哥市估計約有超過五百萬人參加世界大賽奪冠遊行及慶祝大集會，這將是{{le|史上最大和平集會列表|List of largest peaceful gatherings in history|人類史上最大的集會之一}}<ref>{{cite web |last1=Flosi |first1=Nic |title=Cubs World Series celebration ranks as 7th largest gathering in human history |url=http://www.fox32chicago.com/news/local/215601786-story |website=fox32chicago.com |publisher=Fox32 |accessdate=2016-11-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161105005210/http://www.fox32chicago.com/news/local/215601786-story |archive-date=2016-11-05 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。季賽結束後，小熊隊決定進行兩次傳統的[[白宮|白宮]]拜訪之旅：他們先於2017年1月16日拜訪即將於該週卸任的[[巴拉克·歐巴馬|巴拉克·歐巴馬]]總統{{efn|他是[[芝加哥白襪隊|白襪隊]]球迷}}，然後於2017年6月28日拜訪新上任的[[唐納·川普|唐納·川普]]總統<ref>{{cite news|title=President Trump Welcomes the Chicago Cubs to the White House|url=https://www.whitehouse.gov/blog/2017/06/29/president-trump-welcomes-chicago-cubs-white-house|website=[[WhiteHouse.gov|WhiteHouse.gov]]|date=2017-06-29|accessdate=2018-11-03|archive-date=2017-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171214132352/https://www.whitehouse.gov/blog/2017/06/29/president-trump-welcomes-chicago-cubs-white-house|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==後續發展==
===小熊隊===
小熊隊在2015年至2020年間持續取得的成功，是自{{le|死球時代|dead-ball era}}以來最輝煌的<ref>{{Cite web|title=Reflecting on the Cubs’ Five-Year Run|url=https://community.fangraphs.com/reflecting-on-the-cubs-five-year-run/|access-date=2020-12-10|website=Community Blog|archive-date=2021-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114070710/https://community.fangraphs.com/reflecting-on-the-cubs-five-year-run/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但在2016年以後，小熊隊就未能重演2016年10月的奇蹟。{{le|2017年芝加哥小熊隊球季|2017 Chicago Cubs season|2017年的小熊隊}}雖然又再次打入[[2017年國家聯盟冠軍賽|國聯冠軍賽]]，但卻以一勝四敗輸給{{le|2017年洛杉磯道奇隊球季|2017 Los Angeles Dodgers season|道奇隊}}，無力爭奪世界大賽冠軍<ref>{{cite web|url=http://m.dodgers.mlb.com/news/article/259108988/dodgers-rout-cubs-win-nlcs-make-world-series/|title=Hollywood & Vines: LA wins NLCS at Wrigley!|work=mlb.com|last=Muskat|first=Carrie and Ken Gurnick|date=2017-10-19|accessdate=2017-10-19|archive-date=2017-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171025125226/http://m.dodgers.mlb.com/news/article/259108988/dodgers-rout-cubs-win-nlcs-make-world-series/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。{{mlby|2018}}正規季賽結束時，小熊隊與{{le|2018年密爾瓦基釀酒人隊球季|2018 Milwaukee Brewers season|密爾瓦基釀酒人隊}}並列分區第一，但卻在[[2018年國家聯盟中區封王決勝加賽|第163場的決勝加賽]]中輸掉，無緣在國聯中區三連霸<ref name=tribune>{{cite web |url=http://www.chicagotribune.com/sports/baseball/cubs/ct-spt-cubs-brewers-20181001-story.html |title=Cold bats cost the Cubs in NL Central tiebreaker loss to the Brewers |publisher=Chicago Tribune |date=2018-08-30 |access-date=2018-10-02 |archive-date=2019-04-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190406082900/https://www.chicagotribune.com/sports/baseball/cubs/ct-spt-cubs-brewers-20181001-story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。雖然他們後來在隔天的[[2018年國家聯盟外卡晉級賽|外卡晉級賽]]以主場身分，迎戰[[2018年國家聯盟西區封王決勝加賽|國聯西區第二]]的{{le|2018年科羅拉多落磯隊球季|2018 Colorado Rockies season|科羅拉多落磯隊}}，但還是在延長賽鏖戰13局後以1比2敗北<ref name=tribune/>。到了{{mlby|2019}}，他們甚至無法晉級季後賽<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cbssports.com/mlb/news/joe-maddon-out-as-cubs-manager-after-five-season-run-that-included-four-postseason-trips-2016-world-series-title/|title=Joe Maddon out as Cubs manager after five-season run that included four postseason trips, 2016 World Series title|website=CBSSports.com|language=en|access-date=2019-12-09|archive-date=2020-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125023143/https://www.cbssports.com/mlb/news/joe-maddon-out-as-cubs-manager-after-five-season-run-that-included-four-postseason-trips-2016-world-series-title/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但在因[[COVID-19|COVID-19]]而縮水的{{mlby|2020}}賽季裡，他們又成功在國聯中區封王<ref>{{Cite web|title=Chicago Cubs Playoff Update: Potential Opponents Come Into Focus|url=https://www.nbcchicago.com/news/sports/chicago-baseball/chicago-cubs-playoff-update-potential-opponents-come-into-focus/2345392/|access-date=2020-10-12|website=NBC Chicago|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118222226/https://www.nbcchicago.com/news/sports/chicago-baseball/chicago-cubs-playoff-update-potential-opponents-come-into-focus/2345392/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。但他們最終在[[2020年國家聯盟外卡系列賽#邁阿密馬林魚對芝加哥小熊|外卡系列賽]]中遭到{{le|2020年邁阿密馬林魚隊球季|2020 Miami Marlins season|較弱的馬林魚隊}}兩場橫掃出局<ref>{{Cite web|last=Miller|first=Dionne|last2=Team|first2=ABC7 Chicago Digital|date=2020-10-02|title=Cubs lose to Marlins during game 2 of MLB Wild Card Series|url=https://abc7chicago.com/6720588/|access-date=2020-10-12|website=ABC7 Chicago|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113082815/https://abc7chicago.com/6720588/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

小熊隊2016年的冠軍陣容隨著時間推移正慢慢地解體，有些人成為自由球員、有些人被交易，還有些人則選擇高掛球鞋退休。[[德克斯特·佛勒|德克斯特·佛勒]]繼2016年前曾幾乎與[[巴爾的摩金鶯隊|巴爾的摩金鶯隊]]簽約後，這次選擇在2016年至2017年間的休賽季與同區對手[[聖路易紅雀隊|聖路易紅雀隊]]簽約<ref>{{cite web |url=http://m.cardinals.mlb.com/news/article/210732942/cardinals-sign-deal-with-of-dexter-fowler |title=Fowler, Cardinals agree on 5-year deal |publisher=MLB.com |date=2016-12-09 |accessdate=2019-01-28 |archive-date=2017-08-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170822012906/http://m.cardinals.mlb.com/news/article/210732942/cardinals-sign-deal-with-of-dexter-fowler/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[阿羅魯迪斯·查普曼|阿羅魯迪斯·查普曼]]以簽下史上後援投手最大約回歸[[洋基隊|洋基隊]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Yankees finalize 5-year deal with Chapman|url=https://www.mlb.com/news/yankees-sign-aroldis-chapman-to-5-year-deal-c211269270|access-date=2020-12-10|website=MLB.com|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113054316/https://www.mlb.com/news/yankees-sign-aroldis-chapman-to-5-year-deal-c211269270|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年的[[冬季會議|冬季會議]]上，[[荷黑·索列爾|荷黑·索列爾]]和{{le|崔維斯·伍德|Travis Wood}}被送出以換回全明星等級的終結者[[韋德·戴維斯|韋德·戴維斯]]，有效地頂替查普曼的位子<ref>{{Cite web|title=Cubs acquire closer Davis from Royals for Soler|url=https://www.mlb.com/news/cubs-trade-jorge-soler-for-wade-davis-c210494838|access-date=2020-12-10|website=MLB.com|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112212357/https://www.mlb.com/news/cubs-trade-jorge-soler-for-wade-davis-c210494838|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年世界大賽的第七戰對球迷們喜愛的[[大衛·羅斯|大衛·羅斯]]來說也是球員生涯的最後一戰，之後他便宣布退休<ref>{{cite news|last1=Smith|first1=Alex|title=Former SEC star David Ross makes World Series history in final career game|url=https://www.seccountry.com/florida/former-sec-star-david-ross-makes-world-series-history-in-final-career-game|access-date=2016-11-02|work=SEC Country|date=2016-11-02|archive-date=2018-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180816025646/https://www.seccountry.com/florida/former-sec-star-david-ross-makes-world-series-history-in-final-career-game|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。2019年賽季結束後，羅斯取代[[喬·梅登|喬·梅登]]成為小熊隊總教練，梅登在接掌小熊隊兵符五年後與其分道揚鑣<ref>{{Cite web|date=2019-10-23|title=Cubs bring back former catcher Ross as manager|url=https://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/27909976/cubs-hire-david-ross-manager-3-year-deal|access-date=2020-12-10|website=ESPN.com|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113070540/https://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/27909976/cubs-hire-david-ross-manager-3-year-deal|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[米格爾·蒙特羅|米格爾·蒙特羅]]在公開抱怨因[[威爾遜·康崔拉斯|威爾遜·康崔拉斯]]的緊急情況影響上場時間後<ref>{{Cite web|title=Cubs Catcher Miguel Montero Whines About His Playing Time Despite Team's World Series Win|url=https://www.complex.com/sports/2016/11/cubs-catcher-miguel-montero-whines-playing-playing-time-despite-title-win|access-date=2020-12-10|website=Complex|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113213625/https://www.complex.com/sports/2016/11/cubs-catcher-miguel-montero-whines-playing-playing-time-despite-title-win|dead-url=no}}</ref>，他就在2017年賽季間被球隊交易到[[多倫多藍鳥隊|藍鳥隊]]以換回現金<ref>{{Cite web|title=Cubs trade catcher Montero to Blue Jays|url=https://www.mlb.com/news/cubs-trade-miguel-montero-to-blue-jays-c240224190|access-date=2020-12-10|website=MLB.com|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113083540/https://www.mlb.com/news/cubs-trade-miguel-montero-to-blue-jays-c240224190|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2017年也是[[傑克·艾瑞亞特|傑克·艾瑞亞特]]在小熊隊的最後一個賽季，之後他就和[[費城費城人隊|費城人隊]]簽下自由球員的約<ref>{{Cite web|last=Chavez|first=Chris|title=Jake Arrieta to sign three-year deal with Phillies|url=https://www.si.com/mlb/2018/03/11/jake-arrieta-signs-philadelphia-phillies-contract-mlb-free-agency|access-date=2020-12-12|website=Sports Illustrated|language=en-us|archive-date=2021-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112184502/https://www.si.com/mlb/2018/03/11/jake-arrieta-signs-philadelphia-phillies-contract-mlb-free-agency|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[約翰·雷基|約翰·雷基]]同樣在這年球季結束後退役<ref>{{cite web |author1=Andrew Mearns |title=John Lackey toasted the camera from the stands in his return to Wrigley Field |url=https://www.mlb.com/cut4/john-lackey-comes-back-to-wrigley-field/c-296342044 |website=mlb.com |accessdate=2021-01-12 |date=2018-09-27 |archive-date=2021-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113154842/https://www.mlb.com/cut4/john-lackey-comes-back-to-wrigley-field/c-296342044 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。曾在2016年世界大賽助隊抓下最後一個出局數的[[麥克·蒙哥馬利|麥克·蒙哥馬利]]，也在2019年交易大限前被交易到荷黑·索列爾所在的[[堪薩斯皇家隊|皇家隊]]<ref>{{Cite web|date=2019-07-16|title=Chicago Cubs: Trading Mike Montgomery was inevitable|url=https://cubbiescrib.com/2019/07/16/chicago-cubs-trading-mike-montgomery-inevitable/|access-date=2020-12-10|website=Cubbies Crib|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112184502/https://cubbiescrib.com/2019/07/16/chicago-cubs-trading-mike-montgomery-inevitable/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[艾迪生·羅素|艾迪生·羅素]]在被前妻指控家暴後<ref>{{Cite web|title=No Timetable on Finishing Addison Russell Investigation, MLB Commissioner Says|url=https://www.nbcchicago.com/news/sports/chicago-baseball/no-timetable-on-finishing-addison-russell-investigation-mlb-manfred/172374/|access-date=2020-12-10|website=NBC Chicago|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113202342/https://www.nbcchicago.com/news/sports/chicago-baseball/no-timetable-on-finishing-addison-russell-investigation-mlb-manfred/172374/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，他曾一度有希望的職業生涯就在2019年賽季後不被小熊隊續約的慘況中，化為泡影。[[世界大賽最有價值球員獎|世界大賽最有價值球員獎]][[班·佐布里斯特|班·佐布里斯特]]也同樣在2019年賽季後選擇高掛球鞋退休<ref>{{Cite web|last=Gonzales|first=Mark|title=Cubs Q&A: Is Ben Zobrist retired? How would the Cubs fare in a Florida-Arizona split? Any Marquee Sports updates?|url=https://www.chicagotribune.com/sports/cubs/ct-cb-chicago-cubs-mailbag-ben-zobrist-20200419-eeaepoglrffonn3h6h37aftcmm-story.html|access-date=2020-12-10|website=chicagotribune.com|archive-date=2021-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113212811/https://www.chicagotribune.com/sports/cubs/ct-cb-chicago-cubs-mailbag-ben-zobrist-20200419-eeaepoglrffonn3h6h37aftcmm-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。前總經理[[西奧·艾普斯坦|西奧·艾普斯坦]]在2020年11月20日也宣布離職<ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-11-17|title=Theo Epstein steps down after 9 seasons leading Cubs|url=https://apnews.com/article/mlb-baseball-theo-epstein-chicago-jed-hoyer-61107195433d3c47146c87628f877d20|access-date=2020-12-21|website=AP NEWS|archive-date=2021-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113222522/https://apnews.com/article/mlb-baseball-theo-epstein-chicago-jed-hoyer-61107195433d3c47146c87628f877d20|dead-url=no}}</ref>，由[[杰德·霍耶|杰德·霍耶]]接任。

2021年初，小熊隊宣布不與[[凱爾·舒瓦伯|凱爾·舒瓦伯]]和[[亞伯特·艾摩拉|亞伯特·艾摩拉]]兩人續約<ref>{{Cite web|last=Dorsey|first=Russell|date=2020-12-02|title=Cubs non-tender OFs Kyle Schwarber and Albert Almora|url=https://chicago.suntimes.com/cubs/2020/12/2/21959451/cubs-non-tender-kyle-schwarber-albert-almora|access-date=2020-12-21|website=Chicago Sun-Times|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113012005/https://chicago.suntimes.com/cubs/2020/12/2/21959451/cubs-non-tender-kyle-schwarber-albert-almora|dead-url=no}}</ref>。6月底的一波11連敗後，小熊宣布將成為今年交易市場賣家；在7月底交易大限前，小熊於24小時內接連送走[[安東尼·瑞佐|安東尼·瑞佐]]、[[哈維爾·巴耶茲|哈維爾·巴耶茲]]和[[克里斯·布萊恩|克里斯·布萊恩]]三大明星球員，自此小熊隊破咒奪冠班底僅剩王牌投捕搭檔[[凱爾·漢崔克斯|凱爾·漢崔克斯]]與[[威爾遜·康崔拉斯|威爾遜·康崔拉斯]]，以及早已老化的[[傑克·艾瑞亞特|傑克·艾瑞亞特]]和[[傑森·海沃德|傑森·海沃德]]。

===印地安人隊===
對印地安人隊來說，2016年同樣是他們的高峰。他們在{{le|2017年克里夫蘭印地安人隊球季|2017 Cleveland Indians season|2017年}}正規賽季曾創下22連勝，距離大聯盟史上紀錄僅五場之遙<ref>{{cite newspaper |last=Dodd |first=Rustin |url=http://www.kansascity.com/sports/mlb/kansas-city-royals/article173660271.html |title=Streak struck down: Royals beat the Indians, snap longest winning streak in 101 years |work=[[The_Kansas_City_Star|The Kansas City Star]] |date=2017-09-15 |accessdate=2017-09-22 |archive-date=2017-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170923002739/http://www.kansascity.com/sports/mlb/kansas-city-royals/article173660271.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> ，賽季結束以102勝60敗在[[美聯中區|美聯中區]]和整個美聯取得龍頭<ref>{{cite web |author1=Mike Axisa |title=Indians clinch second straight AL Central title |url=https://www.cbssports.com/mlb/news/indians-clinch-second-straight-al-central-title/ |website=cbssports.com |accessdate=2021-01-12 |date=2017-09-16 |archive-date=2017-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170929065905/https://www.cbssports.com/mlb/news/indians-clinch-second-straight-al-central-title/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。然而他們在[[2017年美國聯盟分區賽|美聯分區賽]]上慘遭{{le|2017年紐約洋基隊球季|2017 New York Yankees season|紐約洋基隊}}逆轉淘汰<ref>{{cite web |author1=Associated Press |title=MLB playoffs: Yankees come back from 2-0 series deficit to beat Indians |url=https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2017/oct/11/new-york-yankees-cleveland-indians-mlb-playoffs |website=The Guardian |accessdate=2021-01-12 |date=2017-10-12 |archive-date=2021-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113221249/https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2017/oct/11/new-york-yankees-cleveland-indians-mlb-playoffs |dead-url=no }}</ref>。隔年印地安人隊又在分區封王，但季後賽第一輪又遭{{le|2018年休士頓太空人隊球季|2018 Houston Astros season|太空人隊}}橫掃淘汰<ref>{{cite web |author1=Chandler Rome |title=Astros sweep way past Indians to move on to ALCS |url=https://www.chron.com/sports/astros/article/Houston-Astros-sweep-Cleveland-Indians-move-ALCS-13289918.php |website=Chron |accessdate=2021-01-12 |date=2018-10-08 |archive-date=2020-11-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126074642/https://www.chron.com/sports/astros/article/Houston-Astros-sweep-Cleveland-Indians-move-ALCS-13289918.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>。印地安人隊也和小熊隊一樣，2019年沒能晉級季後賽，但在2020年重返，可是印地安人隊在[[2020年美國聯盟外卡晉級賽|2020年美國聯盟外卡晉級賽]]中再次敗給{{le|2020年紐約洋基隊球季|2020 New York Yankees season|洋基隊}}<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/30013682/new-york-yankees-advance-beat-cleveland-indians-longest-9-inning-game-mlb-history |title=New York Yankees advance, beat Cleveland Indians in longest 9-inning game in MLB history |date=2020-09-30 |website=ESPN.com |publisher=Associated Press |access-date=2020-09-30 |archive-date=2020-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201104204756/https://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/30013682/new-york-yankees-advance-beat-cleveland-indians-longest-9-inning-game-mlb-history |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

